<td>About 50% of mobile visitors leave before the page finishes loading. That is half your ad spend wasted on clicks that never convert.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>4 pages target the same keyword</td>
<td>Your site is splitting its own ranking ability. Google does not know which page to show, so it shows none of them prominently.</td>
</tr>
