<p>Most pitches are lost in follow-up, not in the room. A study by Brevet found that 80% of sales require 5 follow-up calls after the meeting, yet 44% of reps give up after one attempt. The agencies that close the most deals have a follow-up system, not a follow-up impulse.</p>
