<h3>When to Stop Following Up</h3>
<p>Follow up for 60 days or until you get a clear no. A clear no is better than silence because it frees your time for prospects who are ready. If you get a "not right now," ask for permission to check back in 90 days. Add them to a light nurture sequence.</p>
